      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"docs/api/Zaya.OCR.Impl.OneOcr.Services.OneOcrService.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">OneOCR engine implementation of <xref href=\"Zaya.OCR.Services.IOCRService\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> using P/Invoke\ninto the native <code>oneocr.dll</code> (Windows 11 SnippingTool OCR engine).\nNo WinRT, no Windows App SDK, no package identity required.\nCall <xref href=\"Zaya.OCR.Impl.OneOcr.Services.OneOcrService.InitializeAsync(System.Collections.Generic.IReadOnlyDictionary%7bSystem.String%2cSystem.Object%7d%2cSystem.Threading.CancellationToken)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> before creating sessions.</p>\n"
