      "Title": "Zaya.OCR.Services.IOCRService",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"docs/api/Zaya.OCR.Services.IOCRService.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Provides text recognition (OCR) capabilities.\nCreate sessions with <xref href=\"Zaya.OCR.Services.IOCRService.CreateSessionAsync(System.Threading.CancellationToken)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to perform recognition\nwith a fixed set of options.\nCall <xref href=\"Zaya.OCR.Services.IOCRService.InitializeAsync(System.Collections.Generic.IReadOnlyDictionary%7bSystem.String%2cSystem.Object%7d%2cSystem.Threading.CancellationToken)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> with engine-specific settings before use.</p>\n"
    },
