      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Zaya.OCR.Services.IOCRSession",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"docs/api/Zaya.OCR.Services.IOCRSession.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Represents an active OCR session with fixed recognition options.\nCreate via <xref href=\"Zaya.OCR.Services.IOCRService.CreateSessionAsync(System.Threading.CancellationToken)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
